SubjectOrder Fixing Certain Dates as the Days on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the coming into force dates of certain sections of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2014 ACT, NO. 1, chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014, (1) August 29, 2014 for sections 193 to 199; and (2) September 30, 2014 for sections 200 to 204.
